library(ggplot2)

#Create a custom color scale

  geom_point(size = 3, position="jitter") +

The most informative constraints are read from left to right. These are numbers 5, 6, 13. Looking at the summary: - including constraint 5 on average reduces the RMSD by 9.1% - including constraint 6 on average reduces the RMSD by 5.5% - including constraint 13 on average reduces the RMSD by 4.4%

The least informative ones are 14 and 3.
